com.cornell.opencomm.rtpstreamer
Class AudioPusher

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Thread
      com.cornell.opencomm.rtpstreamer.AudioPusher
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable
public class AudioPusher
extends Thread

Reads frames of audio input from a file and pushes them onto designated queues. Generally for use with the emulator since it can't instantiate the microphone.

Author:
Curtis Based off of r473 of Sipdroid's RTPStreamSender class (sipdroid.org).
